title: Match of the Day - S51E07 - 19th September 2015 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD   
Date: Saturday 19th September 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:55 

Gary Lineker introduces highlights and reaction to the day's seven Premier League matches, with studio guests Alan Shearer and Danny Murphy. Champions Chelsea entertain Arsenal at Stamford Bridge, the second meeting between the clubs this season following the Gunners' victory in the Community Shield in August. That win was Arsene Wenger's first in 14 attempts over his old adversary Jose Mourinho across an 11-year period. The day's other fixtures see Manchester City host West Ham, Roberto Martinez take his Everton side to former employees Swansea, Aston Villa play West Midlands neighbours West Bromwich Albion, Newcastle face Watford, Bournemouth take on Sunderland and Stoke meet Leicester.

Running sequence:

Man City v West Ham
Chelsea v Arsenal
Newcastle v Watford
Stoke v Leicester
Bournemouth v Sunderland
Aston Villa v West Brom
Swansea v Everton
